{"tid":2449073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴凍結月票票價","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T03:40:07.000Z","uid":312744,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2289b4c32668e16151d217c29c4815b7922f2c2d","tid":2449073,"uid":312744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"九巴稱，鑑於目前本港經濟情況，九巴決定凍結「九巴月票」票價，維持於780元，令乘客受惠。龍運巴士票價維持不變。<br />\n<br />\n九巴和龍運對上一次調整票價，分別於7年前和10年前。兩間巴士公司於兩年半前申請加價，期間兩間公司未有間斷更新車隊、提升服務，加上國際油價回升，各項經營成本持續上漲。特別在過去一年多，受疫情影響，乘客量大幅下跌，經營陷於困境，龍運的情況嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2738952/九巴凍結月票票價\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2738952%2F%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E6%9C%88%E7%A5%A8%E7%A5%A8%E5%83%B9&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=4b359f51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2738952/九巴凍結月票票價</a>"},{"pid":"3a18e75729a949471fc43e0add93faf3f78775cd","tid":2449073,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">每程只需$9.8</span></span>"},{"pid":"70bbf5ac250e792682f9e5790190edbe5fe3d23f","tid":2449073,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"趁今個月有交通補貼，月尾買張都好😒"},{"pid":"71dc0a07bc9b8a5ed0650ba31643fcb51b75be89","tid":2449073,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70bbf5ac250e792682f9e5790190edbe5fe3d23f","tid":2449073,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"趁今個月有交通補貼，月尾買張都好😒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"下個月無啦咩？"},{"pid":"d057da978551e035e2ff03168e08d67738ef6946","tid":2449073,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71dc0a07bc9b8a5ed0650ba31643fcb51b75be89","tid":2449073,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco